e":"2019-09-05T09:00:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote><em>我們成長為自由人。 沒人可讓一個自由的人下跪。<br />\nWe grew up as free people. <br />\nNo one can make a free person kneel.</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><del>WINTER ON FIRE</del><br />\n《HONG KONG BE WATER》</strong></span></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵站傷亡</span>、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺事件、<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">阻止民主人權法案</span></strong></span>、<br />\n模糊 臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">清朝債主權問題</span></span>等<br />\n</strong>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span>事件焦點<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、美、德 領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n國際審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 <br />\n還原港人高度自治 落實港人雙普選 <br />\n協助<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重新制定</span>民主進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 <strong>高壓滅聲</strong> 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">港府管治班子自治權名存實亡</span>  聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐嚇 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<br />\n重申 <strong><ins>五大政諫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面落實</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: green;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港<br />\n華夏遺珠 高度自治</span> </em></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">人權民主法案</span> 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[center]這不單是 反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>流水革命 元年</div></ins></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8f57a4a9a60ad93a8bc293d1a6724caa424aa529","tid":1543542,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"推 自己一個女仔 唔敢整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5b0605505999480681b03eb308388ac19d31e9","tid":1543542,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"星期四晚做，得星期五比人睇，唔夠<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n每晚10pm 大叫<br />\n每晚8pm去Twitter/ 藍絲page share真新聞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">每星期三晚8pm集體痴文宣同派傳單</span></span><br />\n平日有時間都要痴，但星期三為主"},{"pid":"70ea2f1be4fda75c581be5ebcbbdfc473d9173f4","tid":1543542,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"一路做緊 好累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c900642313d3fa5f15ff4f82db92ee49355b4e67","tid":1543542,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:10:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d891ed638e7481161ac71d65df0e12b809caeff","tid":1543542,"uid":111602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a8871c8f120ec61300b48235d843877651bef4","tid":1543542,"uid":290250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"推"},